parameters.name: Francisco
parameters.teaser: 14 month old boy who presents with intermittent abdominal pain and bloody, mucosy stool in his diaper this morning. He was normal last night.
parameters.clinical_descrip: 14 m/o boy with abdominal pain and bloody, mucousy stool since this morning. The parents say he was normal last night and slept until this morning when they noticed the blood in his diaper and intermittent abdominal pain. He seems slightly irritable and did not want to eat breakfast. They brought him directly to the ED. Temperature 99.2, Pulse 100. Abdominal exam is soft, nontender, mildly distended.
